description: dislikes school intensely and often wishes to be elsewhere.
generally considers teacher(s) to be unfair, uncaring, and/or overly demanding
demonstration of clear, logical thought patterns and a general awareness of surroundings
having little control over events occurring in his/her life and reports being blamed for things that he/she did not do.
difficulty establishing and maintaining close relationships with others and reports being isolated and lonely
dissatisfied with his/her ability to perform a variety of tasks even when putting forth substantial effort
having a poor relationship with parents; may report having little trust in his/her parents and he/she may feel incidental to family life and decision making
having substantial difficulty establishing and maintaining relationships with others
negative self-image, both in terms of personal and physical attributes
having about as much confidence as others his/her age in his/her ability to make decisions, solve problems, and/or be dependable
